name: Meltdown No. 150819
description:
This is an abstract painting that i started on tradicional media using my coping mecanism of scribbling over a sketchbook with ink and pen, that later end up coloring on digital media. The piece represent the diverse feelings of stress and ansiety that went on that day of my aspergers life.

This item includes a HiRes jpg copy of the artwork in a resolution of 6000x7500px almost 8k. The item can be use for personal use, printing or display. This image cannot be use for any comercial purposes. No fisical copy of the original artwork exist.
